                        |
              If Dividend > Divisor 
        Mod10    2bytes ----> Register Y
        Mod10+1  2bytes ----> Register A 
        Register Y + Register A = Result
                        |
              If Dividend < Divisor 
       Ignore the results, Carry flag = 0
